{
  "texts": [
    "Bias assessment frequently showed unmet STROBE criteria.",
    "Clear eligibility criteria and detailed methods could influence reliability.",
    "For example, Gashi et al. [39] lacked defined selection criteria, and Jungmann et al.",
    "[47] had a selection bias.",
    "Inconsistent reporting and lack of blinding in some RCTs, such as Wang et al. [29], impaired internal validity."
  ]
}